<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/48590165-countdown-1945"><img alt="Countdown 1945: The Extraordinary Story of the 116 Days that Changed the World" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1587305955l/48590165._SX98_.jpg" />
